OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1780333563
OL,3,CWhat is the NHS single patient record
OL,4,Cand how could it benefit patients?
OL,6,FMPs will debate plans for a single
OL,7,Fpatient record for the NHS in England
OL,8,Ffor the first time on Monday.
OL,10,FThe proposal would combine GP,
OL,11,Fhospital and social care records,
OL,12,Fallowing healthcare professionals to
OL,13,Faccess information wherever a patient
OL,14,Fis treated and so reducing the need
OL,15,Ffor people to repeatedly explain their
OL,16,Fmedical history.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
