OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1780333563
OL,3,CWhat is the NHS single patient record
OL,4,Cand how could it benefit patients?
OL,6,FThe single patient record is one of
OL,7,Fseveral reforms included in the NHS
OL,8,FModernisation Bill, which is due to
OL,9,Freceive its second reading in the
OL,10,FHouse of Commons.
OL,12,FThe Bill will also abolish NHS England
OL,13,Fand transfer most of its functions to
OL,14,Fthe DHSC or integrated care boards
OL,15,F(ICBs), to cut bureaucracy, reduce
OL,16,Fduplication and free up resources for
OL,17,Ffrontline services.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
