PN,31203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1780333563
OL,3,CWhat is the NHS single patient record
OL,4,Cand how could it benefit patients?
OL,6,FFormer health secretary Wes Streeting
OL,7,Fwill urge the government to push ahead
OL,8,Fwith modernisation, calling the single
OL,9,Fpatient record "one of the most
OL,10,Fimportant reforms of the NHS for
OL,11,Fdecades".
OL,13,FWhat would a single patient record
OL,14,Fmean for patients?
OL,16,FWhat is a single patient record?
OL,26,@qD@POUsD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
