CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1780333563
OL,3,CWhat is the NHS single patient record
OL,4,Cand how could it benefit patients?
OL,6,FThe NHS plans to move towards a single
OL,7,FNHS-wide patient record, bringing
OL,8,Ftogether information from different
OL,9,Fparts of the health service into one
OL,10,Fsystem.
OL,12,FThis would combine records from:
OL,14,FThe aim is to give medical
OL,15,Fprofessionals a more complete picture
OL,16,Fof a patient's medical history and
OL,17,Freduce the need for people to repeat
OL,18,Finformation when receiving care.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1780333563
OL,3,CWhat is the NHS single patient record
OL,4,Cand how could it benefit patients?
OL,6,FThe DHSC says the law could allow
OL,7,Fclinicians to deliver safer treatment
OL,8,Fand save the NHS more than #20 million.
OL,10,FWhen will it be available?
OL,12,FThe NHS plans to launch its new online
OL,13,Fservice in 2027.
OL,15,FIt will be an optional online service
OL,16,Fallowing patients to connect digitally
OL,17,Fwith clinicians across England.
OL,19,FPatients will then be able to access
OL,20,Ftheir records through the NHS app from
OL,21,F2028.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
