PN,31206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1780333563
OL,3,CWhat is the NHS single patient record
OL,4,Cand how could it benefit patients?
OL,6,FHow would it benefit you?
OL,8,FSupporters of a single patient record
OL,9,Fsay it could improve continuity of
OL,10,Fcare, speed up emergency treatment and
OL,11,Freduce the need for patients to repeat
OL,12,Finformation or undergo duplicate tests.
OL,14,FThe NHS has also said that the
OL,15,Fpatients will have visibility and some
OL,16,Fcontrol of their records, but how
OL,17,Fexactly this would work has not been
OL,18,Fdetailed yet.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
