PN,31207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1780333563
OL,3,CWhat is the NHS single patient record
OL,4,Cand how could it benefit patients?
OL,6,FThe changes could be particularly
OL,7,Fsignificant for pregnant women, who
OL,8,Fare often required to go through their
OL,9,Ffull medical history during their
OL,10,Ffirst appointment with a midwife,
OL,11,Frelying largely on memory.
OL,13,FHealth leaders say this can lead to
OL,14,Fimportant information being missed and
OL,15,Fmay be distressing for women who have
OL,16,Fpreviously experienced pregnancy
OL,17,Fcomplications or baby loss.
OL,19,FWhat are the privacy concerns?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
