PN,31208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1780333563
OL,3,CWhat is the NHS single patient record
OL,4,Cand how could it benefit patients?
OL,6,FHealth Secretary James Murray said the
OL,7,Fmeasures will make care safer, while
OL,8,Fsaving clinicians time.
OL,10,FBut the British Medical Association
OL,11,F(BMA) has raised concerns that the new
OL,12,Flaw could allow patient data to be
OL,13,Fused inappropriately.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
