PN,31209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1780333563
OL,3,CWhat is the NHS single patient record
OL,4,Cand how could it benefit patients?
OL,6,FUnder the new plans, GPs would no
OL,7,Flonger be the data controllers of the
OL,8,Fnew shared NHS record. Instead, NHS
OL,9,FEngland would take on that role,
OL,10,Fmeaning it would decide how the data
OL,11,Fis used, who can access it, and would
OL,12,Fbe legally responsible if something
OL,13,Fwent wrong.
OL,15,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,16,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,17,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,18,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
