PN,31210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1780333563
OL,3,CWhat is the NHS single patient record
OL,4,Cand how could it benefit patients?
OL,6,FDr David Wrigley, deputy chairman of
OL,7,Fthe BMA's GP committee for England,
OL,8,Fwarned that the move would "raise
OL,9,Fserious questions about who is
OL,10,Fsafeguarding patients' data".
OL,12,FDr Wrigley said: "It remains unclear
OL,13,Fwhat form the single patient record
OL,14,Fwill take and if it will build on
OL,15,Fexisting technologies, such as GP
OL,16,FConnect, which already opens up the GP
OL,17,Frecord to NHS organisations offering
OL,18,Fdirect care, or if it will require a
OL,19,Fwholesale duplication of existing
OL,20,Fhealth records with control of this
OL,21,Fcopy given to government."
OL,26,@pD@\OUrD@\O]tD@ROU}D@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
