PN,31211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1780333563
OL,3,CWhat is the NHS single patient record
OL,4,Cand how could it benefit patients?
OL,6,FUnder the proposals, GP practices
OL,7,Fwould still have control of their own
OL,8,Flocal GP records, while the new shared
OL,9,Frecord would sit alongside them.
OL,11,FHe will say: "Those who claim recent
OL,12,Fimprovements in NHS performance are
OL,13,Fsimply the result of more money are
OL,14,Fmaking exactly the same mistake that
OL,15,Fhas held the NHS back for years.
OL,17,F"Investment matters, but we're
OL,18,Fcombining investment with reform:
OL,19,Fembracing technology, cutting
OL,20,Fbureaucracy, improving productivity
OL,21,Fand changing how care is delivered."
OL,26,@sD@NOUyD@AOU}D@dO]
